did you want to drive my car				past simple
	I wanted to drive your car last night

why did you want to drive my car?
what did you want to drive my car for?
	I wanted to drive your car because I needed to get the hospital for my friend		---> because -- sentence     make a sentence
	I wanted to drive your car for my friend						---> for -- word
when did you want to drive my car
	I wanted to drive your car every night
where did you want to drive my car
	I wanted to drive your car to mountains and hills every weekend
who did you want to drive my car with?
	I wanted to drive your car with my family
how did you want to drive my car
	I wanted to drive your car carefully
how long did you want to drive my car
	I wanted to drive your car for fifteen hours
how often did you want to drive my car
	I wanted to drive your car once/twice/three times a day/a week/a year



